our human condition

00:07:16.900 --> 00:07:19.480
of interacting with one another.

00:07:19.480 --> 00:07:20.780
&gt;&gt; Ron Charles: Yes.

00:07:20.780 --> 00:07:22.590
&gt;&gt; Joyce Carol Oates: You
know like a typical play

00:07:22.590 --> 00:07:26.940
or Shakespearean tragedy, people
come together and they interact

00:07:26.940 --> 00:07:30.340
and out of their relationship
