00:07:41.450 --> 00:07:45.910
their whole lives may be bound
up together forever you know.

00:07:45.910 --> 00:07:48.450
It may have seemed like
an accidental meeting.

00:07:48.450 --> 00:07:52.910
So life is like a mimicry of a bar.

00:07:52.910 --> 00:07:55.940
&gt;&gt; Ron Charles: Speaking of
haunted, you are, you were,

00:07:55.940 --> 00:07:57.910
