You're in a whole tradition.

00:11:18.950 --> 00:11:20.250
&gt;&gt; Ron Charles: Right.

00:11:20.250 --> 00:11:21.550
&gt;&gt; Joyce Carol Oates:

00:11:21.550 --> 00:11:24.240
So your vampire should be a little
different from the other vampires.

00:11:24.240 --> 00:11:25.540
&gt;&gt; Ron Charles: Yes.

00:11:25.540 --> 00:11:30.910
&gt;&gt; Joyce Carol Oates: But the first
