00:11:30.910 --> 00:11:38.530
that first vampire was
partially like a bat,

00:11:38.530 --> 00:11:41.450
you remember you've seen
Nosferatu that film.

00:11:41.450 --> 00:11:43.520
He's actually a human being

00:11:43.520 --> 00:11:48.280
but partly also an animal
a bat, sucking blood.

00:11:48.280 --> 00:11:54.440
Then the vampire image as it
was sort of modified became more

00:11:54.440 --> 00:11:57.080
and more a seductive image.

