Like there was nothing
seductive about Nosferatu.

00:12:00.160 --> 00:12:01.580
It was really pretty awful.

00:12:01.580 --> 00:12:05.130
But the idea of a seductive

00:12:05.130 --> 00:12:10.920
and handsome Dracula this would
be Bela Lugosi in the movies,

00:12:10.920 --> 00:12:13.980
