00:12:32.850 --> 00:12:37.570
So then the Twilight novels
for young readers I believe,

00:12:37.570 --> 00:12:40.950
the Twilight novels will
show a very handsome vampire.

00:12:40.950 --> 00:12:44.850
So that's interesting
that that evolved.

00:12:44.850 --> 00:12:47.300
&gt;&gt; Ron Charles: And you add
elements of comedy to that?

00:12:47.300 --> 00:12:50.640
&gt;&gt; Joyce Carol Oates: In my novel
