00:12:50.640 --> 00:12:55.170
obviously a romantic figment
of womens imaginations,

00:12:55.170 --> 00:12:57.480
women are imaging this,
this person who is

00:12:57.480 --> 00:13:01.230
so incredibly handsome,
I mean it seems silly.

00:13:01.230 --> 00:13:02.530
&gt;&gt; Ron Charles: Yes but funny.

