not surprisingly not as
much as other states.

00:38:53.820 --> 00:38:55.120
&gt;&gt; Ron Charles: It's been such
a pleasure to talk to you,

00:38:55.120 --> 00:38:57.450
would you take some questions
from the audience now?

00:38:57.450 --> 00:38:58.750
Would you mind?

00:38:58.750 --> 00:39:00.550
There are two microphones here.

00:39:00.550 --> 00:39:02.000
One, we have time for one question.

00:39:02.000 --> 00:39:06.030
Guess it will be sir.

00:39:06.030 --> 00:39:10.740
&gt;&gt; I thought I actually learned
something in one of your novels.

00:39:10.740 --> 00:39:13.860
About a man I thought I knew
something about, Woodrow Wilson.

00:39:13.860 --> 00:39:16.280
&gt;&gt; Joyce Carol Oates: Oh
yes quite a character.

00:39:16.280 --> 00:39:20.760
&gt;&gt; Quite a character and I
wondered how much license did you

00:39:20.760 --> 00:39:22.180
give yourself?

00:39:22.180 --> 00:39:25.660
Did you give yourself
fictional license?

00:39:25.660 --> 00:39:28.180
Did you merely embellish?

00:39:28.180 --> 00:39:33.120
This is the man, how much of you,

00:39:33.120 --> 00:39:36.620
your visceral reaction
to Woodrow Wilson?

00:39:36.620 --> 00:39:39.990
And to what he represented
then in how he acted?

00:39:39.990 --> 00:39:41.290
&gt;&gt; Joyce Carol Oates:
That's a good question,

00:39:41.290 --> 00:39:45.090
this is what my novel The Accursed
in which Woodrow Wilson at the time

00:39:45.090 --> 00:39:48.090
in 1906 was President
of Princeton University.

00:39:48.090 --> 00:39:51.210
Well I did a lot research
and I read his letters.

00:39:51.210 --> 00:39:55.320
And his, some of his letters I
take and sort of change the words

00:39:55.320 --> 00:39:57.900
around a little bit but
those are his words.

00:39:57.900 --> 00:40:01.370
You know he was, I don't want
to completely criticize him

00:40:01.370 --> 00:40:03.460
because he was a man of his time.

00:40:03.460 --> 00:40:07.760
So he was a sexist, he was a male
chauvinist, he was anti Semite

00:40:07.760 --> 00:40:10.060
and he was a racist okay.

00:40:10.060 --> 00:40:15.960
That's just the way they were
but he was also a reformist,

00:40:15.960 --> 00:40:19.530
he was intelligent, he
reformed Princeton University.

00:40:19.530 --> 00:40:22.600
He did a lot of things, I
mean it's shocking today

00:40:22.600 --> 00:40:26.300
that somebody who's a racist
also did some good things but at

00:40:26.300 --> 00:40:30.170
that time it wasn't, it more
or less the way people were.

00:40:30.170 --> 00:40:34.290
So a lot of things that are funny
that he says he actually said.

00:40:34.290 --> 00:40:36.590
